lyrics:
As I walk through the valley in the shadow of bugs
I take a look at my work and realize there's much left
Cause I've been testing and reporting so long that
Even my momma thinks that my mind is gone
But I ain't never crossed a fault and didn't report it
Me be treated like a punk?
You know that's unheard of
You better watch how you're talking and what you're coding
Or you and your homies might do overtime
I really hate to trip but I gotta, loc
Open jira, I extend the sprint for another week 
Fool, I'm the kind of G that clients don't want to see
Just a part of the process, making sure their products work right
